no.geosoft.jwlf

Class DataArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.geosoft.jwlf.DataArray

  • public final class DataArray
extends Object
    Class for holding a list of values of a specific type.

    The class is non-generic for memory and performance reasons: A List<Object> will contain overhead for every object, while the present implementation degenerates to a primitive array.

    In theory it should be possible to make a generic version of this class, but this proves impossible to work with on the client side as the generic type is not known, other than through the valueType variable.

    Author:
    Jacob Dreyer
